		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I never did figure out what exactly was wrong, something must have been shorted and not connected right, but I just redid the whole CHR ROM part and now it works great <img src="./images/smilies/icon_eek.gif" alt=":shock:" title="Shocked" /> So problem solved.

		

		</td>
